                <div class="info">
					<h4>You need a team or contractor to get a job done?</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><%= link_to "Tell us", { :controller => :projects, :action => :new} %> what needs to be done (e.g. "a social iPhone app", "a web-based document management system")</li>
